full_title: Lose My Breath by Stray Kids (Ft. Charlie Puth)
title: Lose My Breath

description.plain:
“Lose My Breath” marks the first collaboration between South Korean boy band, Stray Kids, and famous pop singer, Charlie Puth. On the simplistic, dance-pop track, the boys find themself captivated by one’s visuals and lose track of their senses whenever they lock their eyes between their significant other.

The single is accompanied by a music video, in which Stray Kids travel to places, where they’re followed by water in some type of form wherever they go. The group also showcases the songs choreography in the video during the choruses.
